&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Why Visit Cartagena?
 &lt;div id="why-visit-cartagena" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#why-visit-cartagena" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cartagena, &lt;a href="https://esim.techpawz.com/posts/esim-colombia/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Colombia&lt;/a&gt;, is a vibrant coastal city that blends rich history with striking beauty. Known for its stunning colonial architecture, lively culture, and breathtaking sunsets over the &lt;a href="https://adventure.techpawz.com/posts/punta-cana-adventure/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Caribbean&lt;/a&gt; Sea, Cartagena offers a unique experience that captivates every traveler. The city is a UNESCO World Heritage Site, boasting colorful streets adorned with bougainvillea and intricate balconies that tell tales of its colonial past. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re wandering through the historic walled city or exploring the lively Getsemaní neighborhood, you&amp;rsquo;ll find that every corner of Cartagena is bursting with charm.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Spend a Week in Medellin: Day-by-Day Travel Planner</title><link>https://visa.techpawz.com/posts/medellin-colombia/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 20:34:45 +0700</pubDate><guid>https://visa.techpawz.com/posts/medellin-colombia/</guid><description>&lt;script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-8772455780561463"
